@startuml 调度助手交互时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "RAGPipeline" as RP
participant "Retriever" as RT
participant "Reranker" as RR
participant "LLMGenerator" as LLM

User -> Frontend : 输入调度问题
Frontend -> RP : query(question, kb_ids)
RP -> RT : hybrid_retrieve(question, kb_ids)
RT --> RP : 返回候选证据
RP -> RR : rerank(question, candidates)
RR --> RP : 返回Top-K证据
RP -> LLM : generate(question, contexts)
LLM --> RP : 返回生成回答
RP --> Frontend : 返回回答与引用来源
Frontend --> User : 展示回答内容与检索证据

@enduml
